                    <a href="http://datamapper.org" target="_new">DataMapper</a>, 
                    <a href="http://jquery.com">jQuery</a>,
                    <a href="http://haml.hamptoncatlin.com/" target="_new">haml</a>, 
                    <a href="http://rspec.info" target="_new">RSpec</a>, 
                    <a href="http://mountaindew.com" target="_new">Mountain Dew</a>, and a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sleep_deprivation" target="_new">lack of sleep</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>